author: Disney
description:
D23 Gold Members—don’t miss D23 Gold Theater streaming live from the fan-favorite event of the year, Destination D23 presented by Lug exclusively at Theater.D23.com 

Tune in to two exclusive virtual events:
Saturday, August 30 at 7:30 a.m. PT / 10:30 a.m. ET
Sunday, August 31 at 11:00 a.m. PT / 2:00 p.m. ET

Join the livestream 15 minutes before the scheduled start to join the pre-show and chime into the chat! 
 
Enjoy updates from D23’s Michael Vargo, behind-the-scenes looks at Disney around the globe, Disney on Broadway, the Disney Channel, and the magic of building Disney castles.
 
Not a D23 Gold Member? Join now at JoinD23.com.
 
#DestinationD23
